data.description: Beautiful multi-level 4 bedroom home tucked into a premiere North Grover Beach neighborhood featuring a brilliant layout. Gorgeous hardwood floors run through much of the house with recently replaced carpet in the bedrooms. The two balconies coming off of the main level and primary bedroom give way to a quick escape with sweeping views and plenty of sunshine. The large kitchen has ample counter and storage space, stainless steel appliances, has access to the back patio, and is separated from the very open living and dining spaces by a well placed bar. The living room itself is centered around a remote controlled fireplace and features several large windows which lends its hand towards pleasant views and an abundance of natural light. The spacious primary bedroom is equipped with heated floors, multiple walk in closets, dual sinks, and a jetted tub.     With over 2600 sqft of sun enchanted living space on a sprawling Oak studded 13,800 sqft lot, this property blends the perfect mixture of nature and taste while still being conveniently located in town. Schedule a showing today!
